in. Generating $6.6B in annual revenue and employing 4000 people.\n\n\tAcquisition Rebranding Contract - General Manager\n\tThe Sanctuary Resort, Pattaya - Thailand\n\tJun 2023 - Jan 2024\n•\t5-star 164 room property with restaurants, bar and wellness center, 8 direct reports and a total team of 65 \n•\tResponsible for restructure and rebrand from a stand-alone property to the Best Western Signature Collection and to drive property towards profitability through increased revenue and stronger cost management\n•\tNegotiated owner investment for capital improvements, collateral and overhaul of operating procedures and team to bring the hotel up to par with the BW Signature Collection brand", "experiences/1/jobEndedOn": "1-2024", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Thailand", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "6-2023", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/1/title": "General Manager", "experiences/2/companyId": "22506", "experiences/2/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/2/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/worldhotels/", "experiences/2/companyName": "WorldHotels", "experiences/2/companySize": "51-200", "experiences/2/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:22506", "experiences/2/companyWebsite": "https://worldhotels.com", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "Property General Manager\n\tTawaravadee Resort, Prachinburi - Thailand\n\tMar 2019 - Sep 2023\n•\tMember of the World Hotels Distinctive, Resort with 199 room and full resort restaurant, bar, sporting and conference facilities, with 8 direct reports and a total team of 105 \n•\tTasked with fixing the Gross Operating and Net Operating Profits of the property by driving the marketing and sales efforts to attract business, and significantly lifting the revenue, also to identify, set and deliver on the capital investment agenda, overhauling the people, culture, and operations of the entire property", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "8-2023", "experiences/2/job