n/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALAvT0B0rZ8n1czUQvuWZFLgdZxK5ZK7zQ", "recommendations/1/context": "Matthew reported directly to Alan", "recommendations/1/date": "October 5, 2009", "recommendations/1/description": "I have worked and reported to Alan for over 5 years,during that time Alan has frequently presented opportunities for myself and also other Managers through out the company. Alan is actively accross all levels of the business and his strategic direction cannot be faulted. Alan looks for human achievement at all levels of the business and is ultimately the founder of the Rendezvous Hotel Group.", "recommendations/1/name": "Alan Featherby", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Business Manager, consultant and company director", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/alan-featherby-46385015/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAMmh4sBOs2QtqaHJfQVIE7LCi8tpelTeTA", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Rod  reported directly to Matthew", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "May 5, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "I had worked under the direct Supervision of Mathew Horvat in 2 properties in Perth and Scarborough Beach in Western Australia. Mathew is our AGM and concurrent Project Superintendent of a $65 Million project renovation of 336 rooms, 13 Tenancies Retails of Grand Rendezvous Scarborough Beach Resort/Hotel and Renovation of Rendezvous Studio Hotel at Perth City. Mathew has been extremely pleasant to work for and has become an inspiration for me being the same Driver and Can Do attitude. A straight shooter Mathew has given me the motivation needed to continue aspiring for greatness and continue career advancement. While working for Matthew, I have gained confidence, identified my professional strengths, and learned the importance of developmental feedback.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Rod  D.", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "M.IEAust. PEng. MEP, PMP, M. AIRAH,M.ASHRAE, CHFE,CEM,C